OL,3,C'It would offend public confidence':
OL,4,CWinston Irvine's prison sentence
OL,5,Cdoubled
OL,7,FHigh-profile loyalist Winston Irvine's
OL,8,Fprison sentence for having guns and
OL,9,Fammunition in the boot of his car is
OL,10,Fto be doubled, the Court of Appeal
OL,11,Fruled today.
OL,13,FSenior judges held that the original
OL,14,Ftwo-and-a-half year term imposed on
OL,15,Fthe Belfast man was unduly lenient.
OL,17,FOrdering him to serve five years
OL,18,Finstead, they backed prosecution
OL,19,Fsubmissions that his reputed community
OL,20,Fand peace building work were wrongly
OL,21,Ftreated as exceptional circumstances.
