OL,3,C'It would offend public confidence':
OL,4,CWinston Irvine's prison sentence
OL,5,Cdoubled
OL,7,FLady Chief Justice Dame Siobhan Keegan
OL,8,Fstated: "It would offend public
OL,9,Fconfidence and frustrate the intention
OL,10,Fof Parliament if the minimum sentence
OL,11,Fwas not imposed in this case."
OL,13,FIrvine, 49, and co-defendant Robin
OL,14,FWorkman, 54, were arrested following
OL,15,Fthe weapons seizure in June 2022.
OL,17,FWorkman transported a quantity of guns
OL,18,Fand ammunition to the Glencairn area
OL,19,Fof Belfast in his van, with the haul
OL,20,Fthen transferred to Irvine's
OL,21,FVolkswagen Tiguan vehicle.
