OL,7,FA short time later police stopped
OL,8,FIrvine's vehicle on Disraeli Street.
OL,10,FTwo suspected pistols, several
OL,11,Fmagazines and more than 200 rounds of
OL,12,Fammunition were discovered inside a
OL,13,Fholdall in the boot.
OL,15,FDuring follow-up searches of Irvine's
OL,16,Fhome in the Ballysillan Road area
OL,17,Fofficers found UVF-related badges,
OL,18,Fplaques and a framed photograph.
