OL,7,FAmid criticism at the outcome, lawyers
OL,8,Frepresenting the Public Prosecution
OL,9,FService challenged Irvine's sentence
OL,10,Fat the Court of Appeal.
OL,12,FCiaran Murphy KC insisted there were
OL,13,Fno exceptional circumstances in
OL,14,FIrvine's case.
OL,16,F"This was a man of peace and good
OL,17,Fwork, that was his public profile, but
OL,18,Fthere was a private profile where he
OL,19,Fhad (possession) of arms," he said.
