OL,3,C'It would offend public confidence':
OL,4,CWinston Irvine's prison sentence
OL,5,Cdoubled
OL,7,F"There were no exceptional
OL,8,Fcircumstances regarding the offences
OL,9,Fwhich should not be viewed in a
OL,10,Fvacuum, given the lack of explanation
OL,11,Fby the defendant about why weapons
OL,12,Fwere found in his car," the Lady Chief
OL,13,FJustice said.
OL,15,F"The references point to positives in
OL,16,Fthe defendant's life, including
OL,17,Fpeacemaking and community activities,
OL,18,Fbut they cannot rationally excuse this
OL,19,Foffending behaviour leading to a
OL,20,Fsentence below the minimum term.
